txt.en: 'Onward to greater levels of acclaim among the Lossoth, eh? Well I can help you with enough Reputation to make you an Ally of the Lossoth of Forochel.'
'Alright, soon you will be an Ally of the Lossoth of Forochel. Ready?'
By completing this quest, you will be considered an Ally of the Lossoth of Forochel.
